頂多咪坐30個鍾火車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有本事唔經大路入咪開洗門票<br />\n<br />\n長空棧道，你夜晚行都冇人收錢，但你過到南天門先再講。"},{"pid":"6f01c5d8010e9992bddd60ebc168704ac0ce8383","tid":263120,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早上坐吊車上<br />\n九點幾上到山<br />\n行左七粒鐘  ko 晒所有峰<br />\n<br />\n五點左右落山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/30/131949_39c4a795cb9a70ab6a53adc4327948c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F30%2F131949_39c4a795cb9a70ab6a53adc4327948c2.jpg&h=c3016552&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/30/131950_49051d92d5c8463a5bba62950585fc32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F30%2F131950_49051d92d5c8463a5bba62950585fc32.jpg&h=8d4fe4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/30/131951_49051d92d5c8463a5bba62950585fc32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F30%2F131951_49051d92d5c8463a5bba62950585fc32.jpg&h=6558746f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/30/131951_04a691251e7ff86c9b3a2ac3a78be2bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F30%2F131951_04a691251e7ff86c9b3a2ac3a78be2bc.jpg&h=e833a3d9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n中途有冇玩棧道？"},{"pid":"f6bd69a7fe2d8ea263470d3a445418e8f70287ff","tid":263120,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早上坐吊車上<br />\n九點幾上到山<br />\n行左七粒鐘  ko 晒所有峰<br />\n<br />\n五點左右落山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/30/131949_39c4a795cb9a70ab6a53adc4327948c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F30%2F131949_39c4a795cb9a70